			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Well lately i've been working hard at getting some nice new gear on my Bard, and i used to use Allakazam.com's feature for searching for new items for upgrading. Worked perfectly on my now lvl 60 Bst, which had the stat priorities of AC (5) - HP (1) - WIS (5)...I'm hoping there's others here that use Allakazam's equipment wishlist feature that could point me in the right direction as to what 3 stats i should be looking for in items as a Bard, what values should be given to them (using that point ranking). I was thinking along the lines of HP (1) CHA (5) DEX (5), or AC (1) CHA (1) DEX (1). What do you suggest for bards? 
<br />

<br />
For those who don't know, Allakazam is found here:
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/</a>
<br />

<br />
My current equipment list is found here, what do you think? 
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/profile.html?422887">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/profile.html?422887</a>
<br />
(ya one of these days i'll get a magelo profile up and runnin hehe)
<br />

<br />
Thanks in advance for the advice!<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
