				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Top 3 stats (and values) for bards on allakhazam.com<a name="41660"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 24 04 7:09 AM</span></td>
