				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeah, I'd say focus on AC, HPs, and STA at all levels also.  The Dex and Cha that you need can generally be made up with just certain select pieces to skyrocket it while keeping the good melee armor on.  Suggestions..Tranix crown, 15 cha+Cloak of greater pernicity 25 cha+any tradeskill trophy 50 cha+bracelet of beauty 15 cha=105 extra Cha on four slots.  Plus most of these have nice benefits to other stats as well.  Dex doesn't come in such pretty packages but remember that most melee/tank gear will have some dex on it to begin with.  Then a few pieces like Seawind necklace and such should put you just fine.  Look at my magelo for a few pieces listed.  Still working my STA and HPs myself, but dex and cha are basically covered, especially if I can get my GM trophy.</span></td>
